* Tactic Generation

- The code generation for the tactic is implemented in autosubst2/Src/Autosubst/GenTactic.v
- The implementation only targets scoped syntax now.
- An example generated tactic for λ-calculus is in examples/lambda_calculus/


* Case studies (tested with Rocq 8.20.0)

- examples/poplmark/sysf_pat.v - contains as_apply tactic
- examples/poplmark/POPLMark22_old.v - contains solution of POPLMark without as_apply
- examples/POLMark22.v - contains solution of POPLMark B with as_apply
- examples/eval_inst.v - substitutivity of evaluation relation of System F<: with records
- examples/poplmark_reloaded/old/ - contains solution of POPLMark reloaded without as_apply
- examples/poplmark_reloaded/new/ - contains solution of POPLMark reloaded with as_apply (stlc.v contains as_apply tactic)
- Each usage of as_apply is accompanied with a comment "EXAMPLE <number>"

